metadata.name: Child marriage
metadata.description:
In every corner of the globe, many children are forced into marriage every day.
Do they know anything about marriage?
.
I know a girl who got married at the age of twelve and was murdered by her husband at the age of seventeen (honor killing). she had a child.
.
They have no idea about marriage and enter into a life together.
This is a violation of human rights. But in many countries the marriage of a daughter is at the discretion of the father.
.
This image is a protest art.
Based on a completely true story in 2022
I can give more information to the buyer.
